example.markdown:
User asks: "Reserve 1 unit of ABC-123 if available."

1. list_domains {}
   - Choose domain = inventory.
2. list_features { domain: "inventory" } and list_models { domain: "inventory" }
   - See feature reserveItem and model Inventories.
3. describe_feature { domain: "inventory", featureName: "checkItemAvailability" }
   - Confirm args: { sku: string, quantity: number }.
4. execute_feature { domain: "inventory", featureName: "checkItemAvailability", args: { sku: "ABC-123", quantity: 1 }, crossLayerProps: { logging: { ids: [{ aiSessionId: "8c2ab..." }, { aiRequestId: "f4c7a..." }] } } }
   - If available: true -> proceed.
5. execute_feature { domain: "inventory", featureName: "reserveItem", args: { sku: "ABC-123", quantity: 1, userId: "u-42" }, crossLayerProps: { logging: { ids: [{ aiSessionId: "8c2ab..." }, { aiRequestId: "f4c7a..." }] } } }
   - Returns reservationId.
